        INTRODUCTION BOX
        TO EDIT: Change the text between the <div class="intro"> tags
        TO ADD MORE PARAGRAPHS: Use <br><br> for line breaks
        -->
        <div class="intro">
            The SKARN project is an open-source research initiative focused on making enterprise-grade GPU computing accessible through reverse engineering, custom adapter design, and comprehensive documentation. We develop hardware solutions that enable researchers to deploy NVLink-capable GPU clusters at a fraction of traditional costs.
            <br><br>
            All designs, schematics, and documentation are released under the CERN Open Hardware Licence (CERN-OHL-P), ensuring free access to cutting-edge compute infrastructure for the research community.
            <span class="intro-emphasis">We overcome Enterprise barriers so YOU can have the tools to move the world forward.</span>
        </div>

        <!-- 
        CURRENT PROJECTS SECTION
        -->
        <h2>Current Project Initiatives</h2>

        <!-- 
        PROJECTS GRID
        Each project is a card with an image, title, status, and description
        
        TO ADD A NEW PROJECT CARD:
        1. Copy everything from <a href="..." to </a> (one complete card)
        2. Paste it inside the projects-grid
        3. Update the following:
           - href: Link to your project folder
           - src: Your image filename
           - alt: Description of image
           - project-title: Name of your project
           - status-badge status-XXX: Choose status (new, progress, complete, funding, tbd)
           - project-desc: Description text
        -->
        <div class="projects-grid">
            
