<!-- 
============================================================
QUICK REFERENCE GUIDE
============================================================

HOW TO ADD A TEXT BOX ANYWHERE:
--------------------------------
Copy this template and paste it where you want:

<div style="padding: 20px; background: rgba(0, 217, 255, 0.05); border-left: 4px solid #00d9ff; margin: 20px 0;">
    Your text here
</div>


HOW TO ADD AN IMAGE:
--------------------
<img src="your-image.jpg" alt="Description" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;">


HOW TO ADD A LINK:
------------------
<a href="your-link.com" style="color: #00d9ff;">Link Text</a>


HOW TO ADD A NEW SECTION:
--------------------------
<h2>Your Section Title</h2>
<p>Your content here</p>


STATUS BADGE OPTIONS:
---------------------
status-new      = Green (New project)
status-progress = Gold (In Progress)
status-complete = Cyan (Completed)
status-funding  = Orange (Allocating Funds)
status-tbd      = Gray (To Be Determined)

============================================================
-->
